name: Baby Craft Racing
description:
Baby Craft Car is one of the best and challenging car game. Ride your car in spectacular environment with extraordinary controls and realistic Car Racing physics and surprising suspension.

Baby Craft Car game is sometimes easy for playing; sometimes it’s challenging and sometimes funny.

Ride maximum distance and use your coin to unlock new world and environment. Baby Craft Car game has More than 100 challenging mission with easy to difficult levels. You can flip one on air and flip two on air.

Enjoy!!!
